The aim of this course is to provide information about Estonia, Tartu and Estonian culture and society through films (including documentaries) and museums in Tartu.Objectives/eesmärkid:  In this course foreign students will get basic information about Estonia and Tartu, and Estonian culture and society.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  By the end of the semester, the student acquires preliminary knowledge of Estonia and Tartu, and Estonian culture, by watching Estonian movies and visiting the museums of Tartu - the student is familiar with the main museums of Tartu and knows a collection of Estonian movies.
